      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "QUICK THINKIN' (1) was a last start winner (22.63) at The Gardens who is building a strong winning record. Form here excellent including two wins. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Sure to prove hard to beat. NATURE BOY (2) jumped from the inside and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 2 lengths (17.85) behind Miss Twix at this track. The form from his last run stacks up well. Expected to be in the finish again. MAJESTIC EMMY (8) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when seventh at this track over 300m behind Midnight Dash (18.03) in a Grade 5. Was in the money the start prior. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Has ability and can atone. FIREBALL ZED (7) will be hard to beat with a drop in journey.",
